'''The Homunculus''' is a beast only encountered during [[Tower of Life]]. It was created from the essence of life in the [[Tower of Life (building)|tower]]. During the quest, three alchemists torture it and eventually the Homunculus gets set free. It creates monsters for the player to kill in [[Creature Creation]].

==Trivia==
*{{wp|Homunculus}} is Latin for 'little man' and references the creation of a miniature human being in alchemy. This is contrary to the Homunculus's design, with it being taller than humans.

